---
title: "US16 — Basic exercise effect estimates (computed + saved)"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>WorkoutSummaryScreen / HistoryDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ActiveWorkout / ViewWorkoutHistory
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>WorkoutSession
  A->>B: finish a workout (END)
  B->>C: end()
  C->>E: estimateCalories(weightKg, hours) - WorkoutType rule
  C->>E: end_workout_session(p_session_id, p_metrics)
  E-->>C: calories_burned, xp_gained, streak
  C-->>B: summary stats
  B-->>A: duration, calories, +XP
  A->>B: revisit the session later (History detail)
  B->>C: load()
  C->>E: listEndedSessions(userId)
  E-->>C: calories, XP (as stored)
  B-->>A: same figures - saved once, not recomputed
  note over E: estimates saved atomically via WorkoutGateway end_workout_session RPC,<br/>read back via listEndedSessions → Supabase (RLS)
